t with statistical fluctuations such as those typically observed in\nspectra with a low number of counts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Jun 2004 18:31:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Sep 2004 12:42:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
