nt\nthat is not too strong (its momentum $p_i$ must be small enough to give $2|p_i\nv_k^i|<\\EE_k^2/|E_k-\\mu|$ for all modes). It is concluded that the prediction\nof a very large effective mass enhancement in the middle layers of the crust\nwill not be significantly affected by the pairing mechanism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jun 2004 13:33:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Aug 2005 07:40:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
