remum of the coexistence region in all cases. We outline an argument showing\nthat such behaviour will occur whenever size polydispersity affects only the\nrange, rather than the strength of the inter-particle interactions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Jun 2004 09:50:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
